## Third-party content

Validation corpus (`corpus/validation-2018-2026/`) contains metadata of peer-reviewed publications (title, abstract, authors, DOIs) aggregated from PubMed, Crossref, arXiv, bioRxiv, and Europe PMC. This metadata is redistributed under fair-use terms for research purposes. Individual papers remain the copyright of their original authors and publishers.

Cite papers via their DOIs; do not redistribute the full-text of any paper that is not open-access.
